超过 500 名开发者通过取消游戏货币化来抗议 Unity https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/over-500-developers-are-protesting-unity-by-demonetising-their-games-3500464?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=over-500-developers-通过废除他们的游戏来抗议团结Imogen DonovanTue, 19 Sep 2023 16:07:48 +0000 Gaming NewsNewsVideo Game Culture https://www.nme.com/?p=3500464 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unity-open-letter.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unity-open-letter.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unity-open-letter-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unity-open-letter-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unity-open-letter-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unity-open-letter-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unity-open-letter-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “在没有协商或对话的情况下，你让数百家工作室面临风险”</p><p>这篇文章<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/over-500-developers-are-protesting-unity-by-demonetising-their-games-3500464">《超过 500 名开发者通过取消游戏货币来抗议 Unity》</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unity-open-letter.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unity-open-letter.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unity-open-letter-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unity-open-letter-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unity-open-letter-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unity-open-letter-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unity-open-letter-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>超过 500 名开发商通过取消自己游戏的货币化来抗议<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/unity">Unity</a>的新定价计划，尽管该公司声明<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/unity-apologises-for-confusion-and-angst-after-controversial-fee-changes-3499487">即将做出改变</a>。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/the-future-of-games-done-quick-why-founder-mike-uyamas-exit-is-on-hold-and-whats-next-3490793">Games Done Quick 的未来：为什么创始人 Mike Uyama 的退出被搁置，以及下一步是什么</a></strong></li></ul><p>截至撰写本文时，这封致 Unity 的<a href="https://unitedgamedevs.com/">信</a>已由 553 名开发者签署，信中承诺关闭所有 IronSource 和 Unity 广告货币化，“直到审查新条件”。因此，在 Unity 重新启动之前，Unity 不会从他们的游戏中获得任何收入。</p><p> “虽然我们一直将我们的工作视为协作努力，但这一决定让我们措手不及。你大笔一挥，就让数百家工作室面临风险，而这一切都没有经过协商或对话。”信中写道。</p><p>该定价计划，也称为<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/game-developers-criticise-unity-for-baffling-new-fees-3497182">新的运行时费用</a>，于 9 月 12 日公布。Unity 的目的是寻求开发者和自身之间的“正确的价值交换”，因为每次安装 Unity 游戏时，它也会安装 Unity运行时代码。 </p><figure id="attachment_3441123" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3441123" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3441123" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Xbox-wireless-controller-Credit-Microsoft-Xbox@2000x1270.jpg" alt="Xbox 无线控制器" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Xbox-wireless-controller-Credit-Microsoft-Xbox@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Xbox-wireless-controller-Credit-Microsoft-Xbox@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Xbox-wireless-controller-Credit-Microsoft-Xbox@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Xbox-wireless-controller-Credit-Microsoft-Xbox@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Xbox-wireless-controller-Credit-Microsoft-Xbox@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Xbox-wireless-controller-Credit-Microsoft-Xbox@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3441123" class="wp-caption-text"> Xbox 无线控制器。图片来源：微软 Xbox</figcaption></figure><p>然而，这被认为是对小型工作室可能从其游戏中获得的收入的不必要的限制。 Unity 反驳称，只有 10% 的客户会受到新定价计划的影响。</p><p>这是因为运行时费仅适用于那些超过特定安装次数和收入金额的用户。</p><p>然而， <a href="https://www.wiggin.co.uk/insight/unity-reveals-controversial-new-per-game-install-fee-model/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">律师事务所 Wiggin</a>表示，Unity 的声明可能已经打开了法律的陷阱，并表示“对 Unity 变更的可执行性感到担忧”。</p><p>虽然软件即服务（或 SaaS）公司有权更新其条款，但这在英国并不总是站得住脚。 </p><figure id="attachment_3497200" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3497200" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3497200" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unity-runtime-fee-debacle.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unity-runtime-fee-debacle.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unity-runtime-fee-debacle-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unity-runtime-fee-debacle-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unity-runtime-fee-debacle-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unity-runtime-fee-debacle-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unity-runtime-fee-debacle-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3497200" class="wp-caption-text"> Unity 徽标 图片来源：Unity Technologies</figcaption></figure><p> “根据英国法律，如果服务提供商的标准业务条款中的某个条款允许他们提供与预期大不相同的合同履行，则该条款只有在通过了‘合理性’测试后才可执行，”威金说。 “我们预计这一转变的重要性以及相对较少的事先通知可能会成为争论的核心理由。”</p><p>由于 Unity 在移动游戏开发和整个行业中的主导地位，运行时费用也被认为是“反竞争”的。</p><p>在其他游戏新闻中，泄露的近 40 TB<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/microsoft">微软</a>内部文件揭示了<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/dishonored">《耻辱</a>3》</em>和新<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/doom"><em>《毁灭战士》</em></a>游戏的潜在发布日期。</p><p>这篇文章<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/over-500-developers-are-protesting-unity-by-demonetising-their-games-3500464">《超过 500 名开发者通过取消游戏货币来抗议 Unity》</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
